{"tid":1975904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬克龍：中國處理新型肺炎疫情　發生不為外界所知的事","createTime":"2020-04-17T00:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T01:09:25.000Z","uid":254383,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8875c0a262f36d12814e5b906b80c710fae50718","tid":1975904,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:49:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521075-20200417.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521075-20200417.htm&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10FKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=af58a4af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521075-20200417.htm&h=9cbbc742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521075-20200417.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n法國總統馬克龍認為，中國在處理新型肺炎疫情的透明度不足。<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍接受英國金融時報訪問時表示，中國在處理今次疫情的時候，顯然發生一些不為外界所知的事，被問到中國如何處理疫情，馬克龍表示，不會天真地認為中國處理得很好。<br />\n<br />\n法國至今有1萬7千多人死於新型肺炎，全國確診個案達到14多萬宗。"},{"pid":"6eab0b4fbcdb71a7c70e6d6386462846733005e4","tid":1975904,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://jchann.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/001-30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjchann.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F001-30.jpg&h=344314aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7eddef2487f5781540bb8d9ff90cd73a36af1139","tid":1975904,"uid":108418,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:51:46.000Z","msg":"不為外界所知=elon musk有渠道知<br />\n<br />\n大家競猜下係唔係坑殺病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25745d95ebbbebbdfb5da40b8a435f26a1d3ae1c","tid":1975904,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:04:29.000Z","msg":"同一日<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文：中國需回應新型冠狀病毒如何發生<br />\n<br />\n英國外交大臣藍韜文表示，對於新型冠狀病毒是如何發生，中國不得不回答有關的難題。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文表示，絕對需要以科學為本，進行非常深入的事後回顧，包括病毒的爆發。他又說，今次的流行病顯現國際合作的價值，英國在安排公民返國和採購方面亦與中國進行了良好的合作。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文被問到未來會否對中國進行「清算」，他表示，在這次危機之後，毫無疑問雙方的經貿來往不能像以往一樣，必須問一些棘手的問題，即病毒是如何發生的，以及如何更早地阻止病毒爆發。"},{"pid":"3b9fa7884a85d8ce660de30df9b8baa83a5dc129","tid":1975904,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:05:36.000Z","msg":"掩蓋二十年的內情 <br />\n至今仍未揭露"},{"pid":"5cf7c0bce27980c12715238fe37b8a5892657447","tid":1975904,"uid":61257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:06:50.000Z","msg":"不會天真地認為中國處理得很好"},{"pid":"d22b555d6c124c221a89a178c22d17834959135f","tid":1975904,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eddef2487f5781540bb8d9ff90cd73a36af1139","tid":1975904,"uid":108418,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:51:46.000Z","msg":"不為外界所知=elon musk有渠道知<br />\n<br />\n大家競猜下係唔係坑殺病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:07:29.000Z","msg":"瘟疫一定係燒，免後顧之憂"},{"pid":"05c7aeef5a2964c5537c06782a082ac75d410da6","tid":1975904,"uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:09:25.000Z","msg":"咪又係唔敢講出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班西方國家根本一樣咁醜惡"}]}